<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٢٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4869">عَمْرُو بْنُ عَلِيٍّ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6931">يَحْيَى </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2472">سُفْيَانُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6361">مَنْصُورٌ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5410">مُجَاهِدٍ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2980">طَاوُسٍ </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3732">ابْنِ عَبَّاسٍ </a><span class="special">﵄</span>: <span class="c2">«أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ يَوْمَ الْفَتْحِ: لَا هِجْرَةَ بَعْدَ الْفَتْحِ وَلَكِنْ جِهَادٌ وَنِيَّةٌ وَإِذَا اسْتُنْفِرْتُمْ فَانْفِرُوا.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>